short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extensions shows your current SO-rating

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you calling yourself a developer? Find out that you are a real developer using this extension. SO-rating shows your weekly visits to StackOverflow. If you are always using SO think again are you just copypasting code from there or are you a real developer? Check your SO-rating! Smaller is better! 

This extensions does not use your browser history for any other purposes than calculating your SO-rating.

Feel free to fork my code here: https://github.com/miikkajs/SO-rating.git
